data.title: Conferencia de Presidentes de la RUP
data.text:
The 28th Conference of Presidents of the Outermost Regions (CPRUP) will be held in Santa Cruz de Tenerife (Canary Islands, Spain) on 8 and 9 November, under the presidency of Mr Fernando CLAVIJO BATLLE, President of the Government of the Canary Islands.

This event will mark the end of the CPRUP presidency of the Canary Islands and give way to the rotating presidency by the French region of La RÃ©union, taking over the presidency for the period 2023/2024.

The Conference will adopt its conclusions in the form of a Final Declaration setting out common political positions of the outermost regions.
